Today's task
1. Created orders Table
- Fields added:
- user_id – ID of the user placing the order.
- total – Total price of the order.
- status – Status of the order pending, completed.
- address – Shipping address provided by the user.
2. Created order_items Table
- Fields added:
- order_id – References the order the item belongs to.
- product_id – The ID of the product being purchased.
- quantity – The number of units of the product.
- price – The price per unit at the time of purchase.
- address – Shipping address; typically handled in the orders table.

